				<p>based on the TEI P5 specifications at <ref target="http://www.tei-c.org/release/xml/tei/odd/p5subset.xml">http://www.tei-c.org/release/xml/tei/odd/p5subset.xml</ref>, this ODD integrates Raffaele Viglianti's prefixed version of the MEI's "mei-source.xml" (<ref target="https://github.com/TEI-Music-SIG/tei-mei/">tei-mei</ref>), the TEI-C's <ref target="http://www.tei-c.org/release/xml/tei/custom/odd/tei_xinclude.odd">XInclude ODD</ref>, and draws on specifications in Peter Stadler's <ref target="https://github.com/Edirom/WeGA-ODD">Carl-Maria-von-Weber-Gesamtausgabe ODDs</ref>.</p>
